title: Frank Lloyd Wright Tree Topper—Dana Skylight
description:
Inspired by Frank Lloyd Wright's® (American, 1867–1959) iconic designs, this tree topper will be the crowning jewel of your holiday season.
The design for this elegant piece was drawn from an entry skylight from Wright's Dana-Thomas House in Springfield, Illinois.  Made of laser-etched brass with a shiny palladium finish in the USA.

8 ¼ x 5 in.
